textBeforeTable: Larimer County Sheriff uses DTRS for primary operations. See the "Larimer County Talkgroups" section. State of Colorado DTRS     Project 25 Phase I     No Larimer County public works divisions have transitioned to DTRS.  Some parks operations are on DTRS but most operations take place on VHF. Larimer County Sheriff has transitioned to DTRS for primary dispatch operations.  VHF channel 2 is used as the primary frequency in DTRS dead spots.  FIrenet, EMS north and detentions center VHF frequencies are still being used for primary operations.
